                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It is helpful to be able to run server tests with newer kernels with enhanced debugging as well as ensuring server support is available for future server OS upgrades as well as easing the patch rework by going in smaller increments instead of large jumps.&lt;/p&gt;

